== 翻新計畫 ==
本站與[[畫廊站|畫廊站]]十分接近，故長久以來一直有興建地下人行通道連接兩站的計畫，最近的發展是一項2005年7月關於兩站連通道的研究。<ref>{{cite web |publisher=[[WMATA|WMATA]] Office of Planning and Project Development |author=Parsons; KPG Design Studio; Basile Baumann Prost & Associates |date=2005-07 |title=Gallery Place/Chinatown - Metro Center Pedestrian Passageway Tunnel Study |url=http://www.wmata.com/pdfs/planning/Station%20Access/Gallery_Metro_Center_NoAppendices.pdf |accessdate=2009-03-06 |archive-date=2010-07-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100705100922/http://www.wmata.com/pdfs/planning/Station%20Access/Gallery_Metro_Center_NoAppendices.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>
